  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba4 \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bc2\u0b95 \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc7 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0b85\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bbe.\u0b9a\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The condition of the parents of political prisoners is a manifestation of chauvinist social torture - Bishop Ma. Sattivel",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Many parents of political prisoners are still in adulthood. I do not know their needs. These show the chauvinist social torture, said Bishop Ma.",
        "Those who lost property and possessions during the war are still unable to recover from the grip of poverty. Moreover the struggle of missing relationships continues unabated.",
        "The deception play of the rulers has plunged the mothers of international organizations into blindness and time-strained relations.",
        "Many have shed tears and pain in search of relationships and many of them have succumbed to various diseases and more than a hundred have died as a result of torture rather than loss.",
        "Relatives of political prisoners are worried about when their relatives will return home.",
        "Mothers who yearn for children, children who are waiting for the father, wife who is expecting a husband, mothers who do not know the opposite period of the children with the family burden are only carrying the pain.",
        "Many parents of political prisoners are still in adulthood. Their needs are not known. All this is chauvinist social torture.",
        "Their standard of living is similar to that of those who were physically injured during the war, those who lost limbs, and those who stayed with them. All of this is an outward manifestation of torture.",
        "Also, ex-combatants who are said to be socialized continue to live in prisons.",
        "The relationship of the soldiers must be maintained. They have been forced into this. Otherwise they have no future. There are those who want to act independently and those who have been imprisoned as a re-emergence of the LTTE. This too must be suppressed within torture.",
        "There are also ex-combatants and prisoners who have experienced various forms of torture during interrogation periods and are unable to speak out. The physical abuse and damage they experience is incurable.",
        "There are various levels of society where Eelamites are psychologically vulnerable. The fact is that many people who claim to be recovering from this condition spend their lives with the affected soul.",
        "This is the time for the community to come to the new agenda and travel in a straight line, facing the genocide that declares the diaspora community to have a massive contribution to make. In the current situation the question is who is tying the bell to the cat?"
      ],
